{"id":798850,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mystic_River_(movie)","text":"\"Mystic River\" is a 2003 American neo-noir mystery drama movie directed and scored by Clint Eastwood. It stars Sean Penn, Tim Robbins, Kevin Bacon, Laurence Fishburne, Marcia Gay Harden, and Laura Linney. The screenplay, written by Brian Helgeland, was based on the 2001 novel of the same name by Dennis Lehane.\nThe movie was nominated for Academy Awards for Best Picture, Best Director, Best Actor for Penn, Best Adapted Screenplay, Best Supporting Actress for Harden, and Best Supporting Actor for Robbins.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Neo-noir","surface_form":"neo-noir","offset":34},{"uri":"Mystery","surface_form":"mystery","offset":43},{"uri":"Drama","surface_form":"drama","offset":51},{"uri":"Clint_Eastwood","surface_form":"Clint Eastwood","offset":86},{"uri":"Sean_Penn","surface_form":"Sean Penn","offset":111},{"uri":"Tim_Robbins","surface_form":"Tim Robbins","offset":122},{"uri":"Kevin_Bacon","surface_form":"Kevin Bacon","offset":135},{"uri":"Laurence_Fishburne","surface_form":"Laurence Fishburne","offset":148},{"uri":"Marcia_Gay_Harden","surface_form":"Marcia Gay Harden","offset":168},{"uri":"Laura_Linney","surface_form":"Laura Linney","offset":191},{"uri":"Brian_Helgeland","surface_form":"Brian Helgeland","offset":232},{"uri":"Mystic_River_(novel)","surface_form":"novel of the same name","offset":271},{"uri":"Dennis_Lehane","surface_form":"Dennis Lehane","offset":297},{"uri":"Academy_Awards","surface_form":"Academy Awards","offset":340},{"uri":"Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture","surface_form":"Best Picture","offset":359},{"uri":"Academy_Award_for_Best_Director","surface_form":"Best Director","offset":373},{"uri":"Academy_Award_for_Best_Actor","surface_form":"Best Actor","offset":388},{"uri":"Academy_Award_for_Best_Adapted_Screenplay","surface_form":"Best Adapted Screenplay","offset":409},{"uri":"Academy_Award_for_Best_Supporting_Actress","surface_form":"B